aplus_text: Inherited Rich Traditions. Deep Rooted Values. And A Healthier You.Ayurveda is a rich tradition that goes back to thousands of years. We all have witnessed the miracles of ayurveda in our juvenile age when our elders used various natural ingredients from their backyard to safeguard us from various lifestyle problems. The story of AADAR goes back to three decades when a grandmother (also a vaidya) devised few ayurveda formulations using all natural herbs to tackle issues such as indigestion, blood sugar etc. in the family. Years passed by, but her creations stayed, until one day her grandson self-realized its benefits and the importance of such home grown solutions for wellness. That is when “AADAR” was born with the motive to bring such ayurveda inspired products to the modern consumer; products which are becoming more and more relevant for today’s fast paced life. All AADAR products are Natural, Vegan and Cruelty Free. Today AADAR works with women cooperative organizations to give back to society and bring such hidden secrets to the masses.Have you tried everything in your capacity to get your blood sugar levels in control, but haven’t succeeded? Well, then you haven’t tried AADAR Jeevani capsules. Powered with the unique blend of Aloe Vera, Neem and Haritaki, this proprietary ayurvedic capsules for blood glucose supports healthy blood sugar levels and induces healthy insulin response in the body.  This sugar management formulation has amazing health benefits and works as a body detox. Just two capsules daily in the morning with warm water will ensure your sugar levels are in check.More than normal blood sugar levels is a serious threat to your health and the potential risk of it is on the rise these days due to unhealthy lifestyles. Making Jeevani a part of your life will help you stay healthy. It supports natural blood glucose levels and also helps with healthy weight management - something that people find difficult to maintain these days.The benefits of Jeevani are many. It is known to remove the toxins from the body and also helps increase your metabolism rate, which proves to be effective for overweight individuals. All this together improves digestion and also boosts the immune system. Jeevani acts as a natural body detox and its regular use cleanse your system naturally.Jeevani is a natural and ayurvedic formulation and has no additives or chemicals. Thus it is safe for everyday use. Just have two capsules every morning and stay on top of your blood sugar problems. It also doesn’t form a habit or make you dependent on it. Regular use of Jeevani will keep your sugar levels in control.Aloe Vera and Neem are the main active ingredient in Jeevani. Aloe Vera is well known to promote proper digestion and helps remove toxins from the system, thus enhancing metabolism and detoxification. Neem, on the other hand, acts as a blood purifier and has antimicrobial properties. Moreover, some recent findings published in Journal of Alternative and Complementary Medicine suggest that taking aloe vera on a regular basis can significantly help manage the level of glucose in the blood.The efficacy of Jeevani and its sustained benefits in controlling the blood glucose levels is now supported by various medical practitioners to help people looking for safe and natural approach to manage blood sugar. The patent pending proprietary formulation is natural with no negative effects. It can also be taken along with your other medication prescribed by your practitioner. We recommend a regular use of Jeevani for at least 2 months to see best results.Health. Care. Naturally.Today the problem of abnormal blood glucose level is not just restricted to old age. Millions of people at very young age are becoming a target of blood sugar or are at the risk of being one. Hereditary factors are not the only reason to blame here, and in reality, a sedentary and inactive unhealthy lifestyle is of major concern. Jeevani is an effective ayurvedic formulation devised to control this epidemic by cleansing the system from within and enhancing the metabolism and immunity.After years of research and validation, we have been successful in sharing our so called “Dadi ke Nuskhe” with the world. AADAR has amalgamated the benefits of ancient Indian medicine with modern scientific knowledge in order to a natural and ayurvedic approach to prevent the potential risk of blood sugar problem in individuals and control it efficiently in people already suffering from it.Our efforts have always been driven towards exploring nature’s hidden secrets and transforming into products of daily use that define health and wellness. But we strive to deliver beyond just the products, we believe in delivering the idea and means of a healthy living. And this has made our whole journey a truly pleasant and an enriching experience.
